Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:13.10,tanda-6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur0.5\bord3\fs80\shad0\pos(1820,884)}Hukuman Dewi Vahl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:17.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tahu alasanku memanggilmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:33.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau dan Yang Mulia Raviselle...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memutus koneksi kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:43.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak tahu-menahu soal perselisihan\Nantara roh dan keluarga kerajaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:47.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau juga tidak merasa\Nhal ini akan menyusahkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:49.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:53.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akibat perbuatanmu,\Nkini keluarga kerajaan mengincar Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:03.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen menyuruhku bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:07.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak,\Ndia tidak akan mau mendengarkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:15.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu kenapa Ellen membakar\Nsurat Yang Mulia sebelum membacanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan hanya isi surat, atau fakta\Nsurat itu berasal dari Yang Mulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:26.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami tidak punya bukti kau sudah\Nmenyerahkan surat itu kepada Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Muda sudah menyelamatkanku, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:37.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan hanya ditolong ayahku,\Ntapi juga putriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:41.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.20,0:01:46.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengembalikan posisimu\Nsebagai pengawal Sauvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.86,0:01:47.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa perlu aku ulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:51.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ti-Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku belum bisa\Nsepenuhnya percaya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengawasimu untuk sementara waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:02.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:06.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berterimakasihlah pada Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.79,0:02:18.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.40,0:02:31.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Balvel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.89,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Ellen, ingin tambah minumannya lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:16.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek, terima kasih. Aku mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:18.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Rovel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dicuekin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau mengabaikan Ayah, Ellen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah bicara dengan Alberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah. Pengasingannya juga sudah aku tarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:38.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, tolong lihat Ayah,\Nkau mau memaafkan Ayah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:40.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:41.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:47.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, Ayahanda harus komunikasi\Ndengan orang-orang di sekitar kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:52.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena hal yang menyusahkan\Nbagi roh dan manusia itu berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:59.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal Ayahanda sendiri yang lalai,\Nmenyalahkan Paman Alberto itu salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:02.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa selama Ayahanda\Nmau introspeksi. Sayang, sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walah, walah.\NJadi sulit membedakan mana yang orang tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:18.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku paham kalau Ayahanda\Nmemikirkan kebaikanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:23.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau mau gunakan aku sebagai alibi,\Ntolong diskusikan terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:27.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi tidak sengaja\Nmembalas tindakan Ayahanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balasanmu itu benar-benar sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:35.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, Ayahanda mau bantu memikirkan\Ncara menghadapi si Hati Busuk itu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:36.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Hati Busuk"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudku, pria berhati busuk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}licik, dan kejam,\Nalias Yang Mulia Raviselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata itu sangat mendeskripsikan dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda juga sama-sama berhati busuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejamnya. Kau kejam sekali, Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, sudahan, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ah. Ayah masih mau peluk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:02.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, mari ganti suasana\Ndan main sepuasnya hari ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, Kakek!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:05.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga, empat, lima...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:11.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, mari tunjukkan pada Nona Ellen\Nkemampuan terbaik kalian sebagai kesatria!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:12.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sembilan... Sepuluh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, belum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, kalian sembunyi di mana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti bisa temukan kalian dengan cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:38.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.58,0:06:45.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:52.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada di sini juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:03.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada yang ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:09.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Celaka, kita sudah berlebihan.\NTidak bisa dibiarkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan Kakek membantumu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Ellen memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:37.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, sip. Ayah juga akan bantu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:40.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, Ellen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku sedang main\Ndengan Kakek dan yang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda jangan ikut campur!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:02.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kita bisa main sekali lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu, dua, tiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Empat, lima, enam...\N- Kak Ellen, Ayahanda juga ikut main, dong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:15.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tujuh, delapan, sembilan...\N- Kak Ellen! Dengar, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sepuluh!\N- Kumohon, Ellen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Sudah, belum?\N- Lucu, kita bisa lihat sisi lain Tuan Rovel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ellen? Ellen. Ellen!\N- yang jarang terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, kehadiran Ellen memberikan\Nkebahagiaan untuk kita semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai cari, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oma, apa aku boleh main ke sini lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:41.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, Ellen.\NKau bisa main kapan pun kau mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami akan selalu menyambutmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman Alberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:01.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ikut senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:06.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau terjadi sesuatu, jangan lupa\Nuntuk diskusi dengan Paman Sauvel, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan pernah\Nmelupakan kebaikan Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Paman berlebihan, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:17.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya, aku ingin menyampaikan\Nrasa terima kasihku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:18.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:23.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak dapat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen kurang suka janggut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:28.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Ayah ingin bicara\Ndengan Sauvel sebentar,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau bisa pulang duluan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:39.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, Paman Sauvel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama-tama, kita harus mengurus ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan pertambangan waktu itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa. Namun, kita harus lakukan\Npenyelidikan terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:09:58.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ada benarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:02.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, kami benar-benar tertolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga ini tidak jadi bangkrut\Ndalam masa kepemimpinanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:12.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa, semenjak Kakak datang,\Nkami selalu beruntung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasi sebelum inilah yang tidak normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada itu, Sauvel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kau segera mengundang\Nkekasih hati beserta putrimu ke rumah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunda juga sudah memikirkan soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:28.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku, itu tindakan yang bijaksana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:32.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, siapa perempuan yang berhasil\Nmerebut hatimu itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:38.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pelayan cantik yang terkenal\Ndi rumah makan kota, namanya Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:41.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedangkan putriku bernama Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sebaya dengan Ellen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:51.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sering mampir ke rumah makan itu\Nbersama kesatria lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dia bersikap baik padaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:11:01.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, Anda harus segera\Nmengundang Nyonya Aria ke rumah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:03.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus buru-buru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:07.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, penerus keluarga Vankrieft\Nhanya Nona Ellen seorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:12.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan tetapi, Nona Ellen adalah pewaris\Nposisi Raja Roh milik Nyonya Origin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus memberi tahu\Nkeluarga kerajaan bahwa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keluarga Vankrieft memiliki penerus resmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat Raviselle menjadi raja,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:26.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ia pasti akan menggunakan perintah raja\Nuntuk menjodohkan Ellen dengan pangeran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:27.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:33.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya, aku baru boleh menikah lagi\Ntiga tahun setelah bercerai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:38.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena Agielle,\Nkeluarga kerajaan memberikan pengecualian
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan membuatku bisa langsung menikah, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Anda masih ragu-ragu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membuatnya menunggu terlalu lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:51.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sauvel, bawa pasangan serta putrimu\Nke rumah ini besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:54.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:03.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rovel dan putri Raja Roh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aria, Lafilia. Terima kasih sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak, biar kuperkenalkan padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:32.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia Aria, dan putriku, Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kakak Sauvel, Rovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak Ipar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:41.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jaga adikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:45.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari, aku akan mengantar kalian\Nkeliling rumah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:48.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Segera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lezatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aria bilang, kita hanya perlu mengundang\Nkerabat dekatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah selesai memilih gaun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:33.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:43.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda benar-benar membantu\NPaman Sauvel sesuai janjinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku kagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, ini tidak mengagumkan\Nsama sekali, Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:51.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihatlah apa yang dia kerjakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waduh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:55.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini termasuk\Ndalam membantu pekerjaan Paman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori, Ellen. Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori, kenapa kau marah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia merajuk karena melihat Ayahanda\Ndirayu wanita sembari minum alkohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:15.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:20.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, dengar dulu.\NAku juga kesusahan, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda bau alkohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori, maaf, ya.\NAku sudah kabur, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:31.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu karena lihat sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:36.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini,\NRovel selalu pergi untuk minum-minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:41.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar minta maaf, Ori.\NAku akan usahakan kita bisa sering bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya-Yang benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:45.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku janji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau serius sampai dua rius?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius, dua rius, tiga rius!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Serius, dua rius, tiga rius?\N- Serius, dua rius...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidur duluan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar, aku ingin membicarakan\Nsesuatu dengan kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari upacara pernikahan Sauvel\Nsudah ditetapkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keluarga kerajaan mungkin akan hadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:07.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Ellen.\NApa kau bisa jaga rumah saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik. Aku tidak ingin bertemu si Hati Busuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku boleh pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku perlu memberi tahu orang-orang\Ntentang status pernikahanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:26.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku agak enggan memperlihatkan\Nbetapa cantiknya Ori di hadapan pria lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Selamat tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sesuai dugaanku.\NKeluarga kerajaan akan hadir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:46.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani-beraninya mereka hadir\Nmengingat apa yang Agielle lakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:52.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, pamerkan kebahagiaan kalian\Ndi pernikahan itu sepuasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:53.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak, apa Ellen tidak bisa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:16:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Maaf, tapi dia tidak bisa hadir\Nke upacara pernikahanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.\NIbunda dan Loren mungkin akan kecewa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, ini demi kebaikan Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas pengertianmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:14.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, aku mengantarkan teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:20.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Loren?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:25.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku memaksanya memberikan izin\Nuntuk mengantar teh ini sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:29.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah ingatkan berulang kali,\Nkau tidak perlu melakukan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:31.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan merebut pekerjaan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:34.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Untuk sekali ini saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:47.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kakak Ipar, silakan tehnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:59.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih harus mempersiapkan\Nuntuk besok, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:00.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah boleh pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:11.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:16.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu, lebih baik Ibu membakar atau\Nmembuat seluruh dunia banjir bandang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:21.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibunda, tenangkan dirimu.\NDia calon istri Paman Sauvel, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tidak akan bisa punya hubungan\Ndengan Ayahanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:29.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi wajahnya lumayan cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.66,0:17:32.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau dibandingkan Ibunda, dia biasa saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, apa Ibu bisa menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menang telak, malah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, perempuan itu\Nselalu memperhatikan Rovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Mungkin Ayahanda juga sadar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.31,0:17:54.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tidak ingin dekat-dekat dengan Bu Aria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:14.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayahanda, kau tampan.\NIbunda, kau cantik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:16.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:19.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, kami pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:23.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ellen, dengar baik-baik.\NKau tidak boleh datang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak Ipar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:39.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku tidak sempat\Nmengenalkan kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia istriku, Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:49.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waduh, sepertinya dia terintimidasi\Nsetelah melihat Ibunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:54.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga saja setelah ini dia berhenti\Nmenatap Ayahanda dengan tatapan aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia putriku, Lafilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:19:00.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Senang bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:04.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seumuran dengan putriku.\NSemoga kalian bisa akrab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:07.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ba-Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.75,0:19:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori, lihat di sana. Itulah keluarga raja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pewaris takhta raja,\NYang Mulia Raviselle beserta Ratu Laral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:30.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diikuti pangeran pertama Gadielle,\Npangeran kedua Raselle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:32.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan putri pertama Shielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pangeran pertama terlihat\Nseperti pemuda yang pandai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:44.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak hanya Hati Busuk,\Nmereka bertiga memiliki aura hitam juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:06.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian bersumpah akan saling mencintai\Nsaat suka maupun duka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bersumpah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:10.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bersumpah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:13.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan tanda tangani surat nikah kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa? Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Maaf, aku tiba-tiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Ya, bukan masalah.\N- Suamiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:30.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak salah lagi,\Nitu hukuman dari Dewi Vahl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Si Hati Busuk melihatnya.\NBagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:44.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika orang-orang menyadari hukuman itu,\Npernikahan ini akan dibatalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:47.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, akan tersebar rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang mengatakan keluarga Vankrieft\Nditinggalkan Dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada cara untuk mengalihkan\Nperhatian tamu dari hukuman Dewi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:01.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sungguh baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:12.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nomor atom enam,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:22.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pernikahan keluarga Vankrieft memang beda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:28.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini anugerah dari Dewi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:37.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Kakak meminta tolong kepada roh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantiknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan, ini ulah Ellen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:48.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya semua lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:52.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ketahuan Ayahanda dan Ibunda.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:55.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cantik, bukan, Gadielle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah keluarga yang diberkati oleh roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:01.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya semua sudah aman,\Naku harus segera pulang...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:11.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
